""SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t0].[TrainingTypeName], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], COUNT(CASE
    WHEN [t1].[ID] > 0 THEN 1
END) AS [NoOfDocuments]
FROM [ajt].[TrainingInfo] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingType] AS [t0] ON [t].[TrainingTypeID] = [t0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingDocuments] AS [t1] ON [t].[ID] = [t1].[TriningID]
WHERE ((([t1].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([t1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))

""SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t0].[TrainingTypeName], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], COUNT(CASE
    WHEN [t1].[ID] > 0 THEN 1
END) AS [NoOfDocuments]
FROM [ajt].[TrainingInfo] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingType] AS [t0] ON [t].[TrainingTypeID] = [t0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingDocuments] AS [t1] ON [t].[ID] = [t1].[TriningID]
WHERE ((([t1].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([t1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))

""SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t0].[TrainingTypeName], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], COUNT(CASE
    WHEN [t1].[ID] > 0 THEN 1
END) AS [NoOfDocuments]
FROM [ajt].[TrainingInfo] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingType] AS [t0] ON [t].[TrainingTypeID] = [t0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingDocuments] AS [t1] ON [t].[ID] = [t1].[TriningID]
WHERE ((([t1].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([t1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))

FROM [ajt].[TrainingInfo] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingType] AS [t0] ON [t].[TrainingTypeID] = [t0].[ID]
INNER JOIN [ajt].[TrainingDocuments] AS [t1] ON [t].[ID] = [t1].[TriningID]
WHERE (((([t].[TrainingTypeID] = @__TrainingTypeID_0) AND ([t1].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([t].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))
GROUP BY [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], [t0].[TrainingTypeName]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t0].[TrainingTypeName], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], COUNT(CASE

END) AS [NoOfDocuments]

""SELECT [t].[ID], [t].[TrainingTypeID], [t0].[TrainingTypeName], [t].[TrainingName], [t].[TrainingDescription], COUNT(CASE

END) AS [NoOfDocuments]

END) AS [NoOfDocuments]
